nrolling in this course are expected to have sound working knowledge of Operating systems (MS Windows) and MS word. This is fundamental course for AutoCAD so basic knowledge of basic design methodology and terminology is preferred.</p>\n\n<p>SYLLABUS</p>\n\n<p><strong>MODULE 1:&nbsp;</strong>AUTO CAD TRAINING (COMPUTER AIDED DESIGN AND DRAFTING) SYLLABUS</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Introduction to CAD Components. (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Hardware, software, basic knowledge in Auto-CAD, drawing icons, pull down menus &amp; other basic concept of drawing utilities used in CAD.</li>\n	<li><strong>Creating Drawings (Setting of Drawing) (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Units, Limits, Snap grid ortho, Dimension style, polar, saving types etc.</li>\n	<li><strong>Coordinate System (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>World / Global /Absolute / Relative/ Polar Coordinate System.</li>\n	<li><strong>Drawing commands /objects toolbar (4 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Several commands are there (in horizontal/vertical toolbar), which are line, points,Text,Solid filled Polyline Mline/ Multiline, Hatching,Construction line,Spline, Explode and related tutorilas etc.</li>\n	<li><strong>Display of Drawing (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Regen, Redraw, Zoom, Pan View, Viewports and related tutorials etc.</li>\n	<li><strong>Selecting &amp; Editing of Drawing objects (4 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Various types of objects selection method, Erase, Copy, Move, Mirror, Offset and related tutorilas etc.</li>\n	<li><strong>Organization of Drawing Works (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Linetypes, Colours ,Layers and related tutorials etc.</li>\n	<li><strong>Information in grouping of objects (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Creating blocks, W block and related tutorials etc.</li>\n	<li><strong>Placement of text &amp; Dimensioning,Editing of Text &amp; Dimensioning etc. (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Drafting of different Components (6 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>basically building drawing drafting based above tools like: Plans, elevations, sections and various types of related Tutorials etc.</li>\n	<li><strong>Method of Plotting &amp; Printing (2 hrs)</strong></li>\n	<li>Plotting through Model Space and layout Space using proper scale.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Reference Books:</strong><br />\nSoftware manuals are to be announced depending on instructors.</p>\n', '0def78ee3f5ca9b4be48d56a76d1446fautocad-2018.png', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 62, 45, 1, 'Courses', 'T', '0', '0', '2018-12-19 00:08:02', '2019-03-25 02:25:03', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 1, '0', 0, '', '', '', NULL, 0),
