(94, 'Research & Protyping', 'research---protyping', '1', 'Research & Protyping', '<p><strong>Research &amp; Prototyping</strong></p>\n\n<p>We develop professional and intuitive websites and applications. To establish your organization as the best company to do business among its peers in the industry.</p>\n\n<p>TechRoadians creative team of designers will first create a sitemap and color homepage concepts. The concepts will then be revised down to one, final design for the creation of the website.<br />\nThe usability and navigation of the site will be of utmost importance in the organizational architecture of the site. Therefore, the team will coordinate with you to streamline the navigation, categorize and group information as appropriate. A thorough review of existing and newly planned content will also be taken into consideration.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Domain Registration &amp; Hosting</strong></p>\n\n<p>We register number of Domain Names and Provide Sophisticated Linux Hosting Servers. To Check for a domain and/or place your order, please visit our Customer Relationship Management Section.<br />\nWe also manages hosting services. This may include setup of the necessary hardware and software on the web server, hosting of the web pages and database associated with websites, monthly backups, maintenance and troubleshooting.<br />\nYour websites are weekly backed up onto cloud so that you will never need to worry about information loss.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/domain.png\" style=\"height:257px; width:465px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/content-management.png\" style=\"height:260px; width:466px\" /></p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<p><strong>Content Management System (CMS)</strong></p>\n\n<p>We provide easy-to-use, robust content management system, simply called CMS. The CMS allows non-technical staff members to add, edit or delete content areas of the web site based on the individual user&rsquo;s role-based permissions in the system. The CMS is also enabled with an approval-routing feature for maximum security and content verification.<br />\nYou will have complete control over the direction of the content of the website and will no longer be dependent upon TechRoadians to make updates quickly. [If that is the need, we always are ready to do it for you as well] With minimal training and documentation, staffs will be able to change text and image elements of the pages on the web site, and add new pages using a simple web-based browser. Members with experience using MS Word and surfing the web will find using the CMS especially convenient for keeping the web site updated and current.</p>\n', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', NULL, 2, 15, 1, 'Page', 'T', '1', '0', '2018-12-20 00:04:47', '2018-12-20 22:30:58', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 1, '0', 0, '', '', '', NULL, 0),
(95, 'Web and Mobile', 'web-and-mobile', '1', 'Web and Mobile', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>E-Commerce Solutions</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/ecommerce-1.png\" style=\"float:left; height:299px; width:343px\" /></p>\n\n<p>E-Commerce are businesses that occur online. E-commerce is also the quickest medium of Business-to-Business / Business-to-Client Communication. Goods, Products and Cash values are exchanged via e-commerce.</p>\n\n<p>We have a team specialized in developing E-Commerce.</p>\n\n<p>Not only big businesses but small and medium businesses such as a mobile shop, an electronics store, a departmental store or even a grocery shop can have an e-commerce. We learn and understand your business to develop a suitable e-commerce system for you.</p>\n\n<p>Developing e-commerce is sales aspect of Business.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mobile Applications</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/mobile-app.png\" style=\"float:right; height:325px; width:540px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In a few years to come, most people in the world will be carrying Internet in their pocket. Surfing Internet and accessing web applications will go handy. People will not longer prefer large and power consuming desktops and laptops for common purpose.</p>\n\n<p>Tablets and mobiles are massively into trends. To cope with the change, e-businesses are shifting themselves into mobile-friendly platforms. There is where, you feel the need of Mobile Applications.Mobile Applications are light weight, easy to use &amp; robust packages that are designed to communicate to your users and business functions. If your business involves significant customer/client interactions, Mobile Applications should be the next consideration for you.</p>\n\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Web Design &amp; Development</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/web-app.png\" style=\"float:left\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We develop professional and intuitive websites and applications. To establish your organization as the best company to do business among its peers in the industry. TechRoadians creative team of designers will first create a sitemap and color homepage concepts. The concepts will then be revised down to one, final design for the creation of the website.</p>\n\n<p>The usability and navigation of the site will be of utmost importance in the organizational architecture of the site. Therefore, the team will coordinate with you to streamline the navigation, categorize and group information as appropriate. A thorough review of existing and newly planned content will also be taken into consideration.</p>\n\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Graphics Exertion</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/graphic.png\" style=\"float:right; height:277px; width:247px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Graphics has a power to influence. Life can be perceived in an object by means of graphics. Here at TechRoadians, we have a professional team of Graphics Designers who pull out from the universe, the best and ever made Concepts.</p>\n\n<p>The scope of graphics can be found everywhere.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Logo Design</li>\n	<li>Brochure and paperwork</li>\n	<li>User interactivity on websites</li>\n	<li>Banners, hangers and materials</li>\n	<li>Enhancing Multimedia</li>\n</ul>\n', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', NULL, 2, 16, 1, 'Page', 'T', '1', '0', '2018-12-20 00:12:03', '2018-12-20 22:32:15', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 1, '0', 0, '', '', '', NULL, 0),
(96, 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing', '1', 'Digital Marketing', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Search Engine Optimization</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/seo.png\" style=\"float:left; height:325px; width:540px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is the art of indexing websites on search engines like Google, Yahoo, Bing etc. The value is then added, when websites are displayed on the top of the search pages. Search Engine Optimization is the work of experts. At TechRoadians, we have a team of SEO specialists, who have proven records.The matter of fact is that websites get popular, they earn real visitors only after they are well indexed and ranked on search engines. Our team works on the specifications supplied by the internet search giant, Google.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Social Media Marketing</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/smm.png\" style=\"float:right\" />&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Social Media Marketing (SMM) is hottest trend of marketing your business today. This service replaces the old email marketing, link exchange and some of search engine optimization techniques. In a short period, SMM has proven its value.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What basically is done?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Your best products or services are pushed into social networking websites such as Facebook, Twitter, Google+, LinkedIn, Foursquare etc. in a continuous fashion. (2 or more updates per day). This generates instant visitors to your website. Moreover, the real benefit arrives when the friends and families (circles) of your existing clients/consumers get to know about your business.</p>\n\n<p>For this purpose, we create graphical designs, use the images of your website and push them together with some text and links. Your Business can also be promoted by means of events and competition.</p>\n\n<p>Our clients are highly satisfied with this service. Your new business is required to push into the market, thus we&rsquo;d like to recommend this service for your Business.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">Email Marketing</h2>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/email.png\" style=\"float:right; height:311px; width:395px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Email marketing is the beneficial and effective internet marketing tool for any business company. Marketing effort for your company can&rsquo;t be complete without email marketing and newsletter subscribing service.</p>\n\n<p>Email marketing is the &nbsp;beneficial and effective &nbsp;internet marketing tool for any business company. Marketing effort &nbsp;for your company can&rsquo;t be complete without &nbsp;email marketing and newsletter subscribing service. In today&rsquo;s internet world, email has become a &nbsp;tremendous medium for all business houses. Similarly, it maintain height of communication &nbsp;between different party, customer, company and business.If you planning to run your business through cost effective way, &nbsp;email marketing should be your first choice.It has heaps of advantage and it helps you to reach between your potential customer.</p>\n\n<p>Sending &nbsp;mass email to your customer is not well enough to &nbsp;get back your investment (ROI). Your email should carry a valuable information and quality content. In order to create systematic platform for email marketing you &nbsp;need to have &nbsp;experienced team.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Ads Management</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://techroadians.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/ads-management.png\" style=\"float:right\" />Pay Per Click Ads management is the process of supervising the campaigns that seek to persuade and fascinate customers about particular goods or service. The main purpose of advertising is to convey and sell the product.</p>\n\n<p>The product gets its image only after the proper advertisement management system so in this technological world advertisement is a must. No business can be fruitful until it pursue proper media campaigns. The success behind any business firms is the appropriate advertisement campaigns according to the changing modern trend.</p>\n\n<p>Advertising is the only way to communicate with customers, which helps in generating revenue and increasing sales mostly it plays an essential role to aware the public. In this technological world, it&rsquo;s pretty hard to approach customers using traditional marketing concept so it&rsquo;s time for you to move with the modern trend. Now, the alteration of technology has made possible to manage your advertising business by using various advertising services. This services helps the manager and executives to update and organize accounts and tasks. If you are concerned about managing your advertising through server you can find several companies with these services. This management system boosts your target market and create an image of your product which is created by the target market.</p>\n\n<p>NUCI can provide you various solutions about the management of advertisement; it&rsquo;s one of the leading and successful company. We mainly focus on providing you advertising services which meet your business goals and make you stable in the market for longer period.</p>\n', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', NULL, 2, 17, 1, 'Page', 'T', '1', '0', '2018-12-20 00:23:32', '2018-12-20 05:31:08', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 1, '0', 0, '', '', '', NULL, 0),
