(113, 'Shah Rukh Khan\'s next role will be as sexy as we want!', 'shah-rukh-khan\'s-next-role-will-be-as-sexy-as-we-want!', '1', 'Shah Rukh Khan\'s next role will be as sexy as we want!', '<p>Shah Rukh Khan was last seen in Zero with Anushka Sharma and Katrina Kaif in pivotal roles. Zero went as a disaster in Box Office as it couldn&#39;t take market as expected. After Zero there were speculations that he&#39;ll be seen in biopic of Rakesh Sharma which was titled &#39;Saare Jahaan Se Achcha&#39; but he opted out of it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After he backed out of the project, there weren&#39;t any reports regarding his next project. Recently, he was felicitated with an honorary doctorate from University of Law, London. He talked in the event, about his next project and said that his role in the next movie will be as sexy as we want it to be.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He said, &quot;My next role will be as sexy as my last one. So you want me to be a sexy father, a sexy hero, sexy whatever you want me to be. My next role will be as sexy as you want me to be.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In an interview recently, he talked about how the workplace in Hindi Film Industry is changing drastically. He said, &quot;The roles of women and the kind of attitude you have at the workplace for women is changing for positive. There will be discrepancies and ups and downs too. There were times when I was working in the &#39;90s that if a lady got married, she normally did not have the opportunity to come back and act in a film but now all of them are acting in films and it&#39;s so seamless and nice, so I think lots of positive stuff for female actors in the film industry.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After the failure of Zero, Shah Rukh Khan has become choosy for roles. Shah Rukh Khan&#39;s next movie is still a mystery but we can be sure that he&#39;ll be giving his best to prove himself the King of Romance again.</p>\r\n', '12b1461e1cfb1bb5af2301f8796a628e1833629745.jpeg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-03 11:05:07', '2019-04-08 08:22:09', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, 'b6d1e8ddb0cfc6234725812399cd55dfdownload.jpg', 'sanghars giri', '', NULL, 0);
