(114, 'Taapsee feels like \'alien\' during the shoot of Saand Ki Aankh!', 'taapsee-feels-like-\'alien\'-during-the-shoot-of-saand-ki-aankh!', '1', 'Taapsee feels like \'alien\' during the shoot of Saand Ki Aankh!', '<p>Taapsee Pannu is currently shooting for Saand Ki Aankh. Saand Ki Aankh is the movie about two world&#39;s oldest sharp-shooters from India Chandro and Prakashi Tomar. &nbsp;She said that she decided to sign the project as its story touched her heart.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Actress Bhumi Pednekar will be seen with Taapsee in the movie. But Taapsee feels like alien during the shooting of the film as her character has nothing related to her background.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She said, &quot;When I do a film I relate to one thing in a character to start off but here there is not a single thing I can relate to. My age, background, the language is not similar; I am not fond of shooting as well.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She further added, &quot;Everything is alien to me. But it is a beautiful script that touched my heart and I couldn&#39;t say no to it. If this film works then people will remember us for life or maybe they will laugh at us.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;I spent a few weeks learning shooting. The most taxing thing was to get the body language of a 60-65 year-old woman right. They are Haryanvi but based out of UP, there is an interesting crossover of Haryanvi and Hindi of UP. But we had to keep it simple for the audiences to understand,&#39;&#39; she added.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She concluded saying, &quot;My Hindi is good because I have lived in Delhi. I have heard Haryanvi before but never tried speaking it. It was a challenge to learn it. I had to behave like a mother and grandmother. These are the emotions I have never experienced. Every scene is a challenge.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Taapsee said that 85 percent of the film will portray them as old woman. It is produced by Reliance Entertainment, Anurag Kashyap and Nidhi Parmar. It is being directed by debutant Tushar Hiranandani.</p>\r\n', 'e961bdecfaff8a82b1ced3f012ac65292005538950.jpeg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-03 11:39:17', '2019-04-08 08:21:13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, 'a3b087a27188baf166f089b40e0da773983794168.jpg', 'sanghars giri', '', NULL, 3),
