(131, 'I want to do a love story with female protagonist: John Abraham', 'i-want-to-do-a-love-story-with-female-protagonist:-john-abraham', '1', 'I want to do a love story with female protagonist: John Abraham', '<p>John Abraham is currently busy promoting his upcoming movie, Romeo Akbar Walter. He is mostly known for his action movies and patriotic roles. He recently said that he has always been offered to do a love story with a male lead and he wants to do a film with a female actress. He added he wants to do a movie with the female actor in lead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He said, &quot;The funny thing is that the love stories that have been offered to me have been with men. I did Garam Masala in 2005 with Akshay Kumar, Dostana with Abhishek, and recently Dishoom with Varun Dhawan. So, I am learning to do a love story with a female protagonist opposite me.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>John Abraham recently opened his own production house. He will be soon seen in Romeo Akbar Walter (RAW). Along with John, Romeo Akbar Walter also features Mouni Roy and Jackie Shroff. John is playing the role of a spy who goes undercover in Pakistan. Romeo Akbar Walter released today.</p>\r\n', 'f1151b1b89efbc90a9bdcd6dd069710c812387381.png', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-04 08:35:16', '2019-04-08 08:25:32', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, '', 'sanghars giri', '', NULL, 1),
