(140, 'India agrees that their plane was attacked by Pakistan!', 'india-agrees-that-their-plane-was-attacked-by-pakistan!', '1', 'India agrees that their plane was attacked by Pakistan!', '<p>India agreed that Pakistan attacked and crashed the jet of Air Force India. Spokesperson of Foreign Affairs India, Ravish Kumar did Press Conference and confirmed the news.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He said that Pakistan did this because of the air strike held yesterday. He also said that Indian Militant also have one of the plane of Pakistan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During the attack, he said, &quot;Pakistan destroyed a jet and one of our pilot is missing.&quot; Pakistan said that they captured two jets. Pakistan also released 46-seconds video.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is a blindfolded man in the video. The man is recognized as Wing Commander of Indian Air Force Abhinandan. In the video, he says: I&#39;m office of Indian Air Force. My service number is 27981.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>India has not yet talked about the video.</p>\r\n', '3caf07eb90bdc7202400bdae5b3e5764850886422.jpeg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-08 07:36:21', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, '', 'India agrees that their plane was attacked by Pakistan!', '', NULL, 0),
(141, 'Will Singha Durbar rise again?', 'will-singha-durbar-rise-again?', '1', 'Will Singha Durbar rise again?', '<p>After 4 years of devastating earthquake in 2015, Singha Durbar was confirmed unsafe and it was condemned by the concerned officials. Made by Chandra Shamsher about a decade ago, Singha Durbar was run by Rana Dynasty till 1953. After Mohan Shamsher left the palace, it was considered National Property and was given to hold different ministries and government offices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But after the earthquake and being considered unsafe, the renovation of the palace was planned. It has already 4 years of the calamity and now the renovation process has started.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is not the first time, though. In 9th July, 1973 too when Durbar caught the fire, it was renovated again by rebuilding under the same old foundation. The palace made in 1908 has suffered many calamities and have gone for renovations for few times. Historically, after 1973 it is being rebuilt for second time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By using the technology of retro fitting, rebuilding process has started recently. Retro Fitting process means the addition of new technology and features into old foundations. Retro Fitting works on the process of strengthening older buildings in order to make them earthquake resistant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After the Retro Fitting process, Singha Durbar is said to be earthquake resistant. The process will undergo in the weaker part of foundations and implants the new technologies and features to prove them strong for any calamities coming in near future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Singha Durbar may come in its original avatar again after the fitting process but will it still be capable to prove its essence after the improvised systems too? Retro Fitting guarantees that the maintenance costs will be reduced and reliability will be increased.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But the same process was applied earlier too after the fire of 1973. Doubting on the same infrastructure can obviously be an alternative regarding the circumstances which were suffered so authorities concerned with the renovation may have thought something about it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Otherwise, the whole budget separated for the renovating process will go on vain and we don&rsquo;t want that. Singha Durbar will rise again and it will rise better because that is what retro fitting guarantees us.</p>\r\n', '967aef54f65bca597122982776f575271784771984.jpeg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-08 07:37:22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, '', 'Will Singha Durbar rise again?', '', NULL, 0),
(142, 'Saif Ali Khan praised Imtaiz\'s Ali next movie!', 'saif-ali-khan-praised-imtaiz\'s-ali-next-movie!', '1', 'Saif Ali Khan praised Imtaiz\'s Ali next movie!', '<p>Saif Ali Khan who was rumored to be the part of Imtiaz Ali next movie recently in a media interaction talked about it. He praised the director, star cast and the movie. Sara Ali Khan and Kartik Aaryan will be featured in pivotal role in this movie. It will be the sequel of Love Aaj Kal and it is titled Love Aaj Kal 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saif Ali is happy that his daughter Sara Ali Khan is teaming up with talented director like Imtiaz Ali within a year of launch. He talked about the movie saying, &ldquo;It&rsquo;s a lovely movie and I&rsquo;m very excited in particular that Sara is working with Imtiaz Ali. I wish both the young stars Sara and Kartik Aaryan the best.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There were reports earlier that Saif Ali Khan will be seen in the role of Kartik&#39;s father in the movie. Saif Ali Khan was seen in the first installment of the movie. It was romantic-comedy movie which released on 2009. He was seen with Deepika Padukone and Rishi Kapoor. Love Aaj Kal 2 is scheduled to release around the end of this year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saif further added, &ldquo;I&rsquo;d honestly want to play every role provided it&rsquo;s interesting enough and if the time permitted it. Though Imtiaz was very kind to offer me a part in the sequel of &lsquo;Love Aaj Kal&rsquo;, I haven&rsquo;t signed the film contrary to the rumours.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the work front, Saif Ali Khan will be seen in many projects this year like Sacred Games 2, Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior, Bhoot Police, Hunter and others.</p>\r\n', '9b271f0acad5b485cc5cee3a13131a5f166956240.jpeg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-08 07:38:04', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, '', 'Saif Ali Khan praised Imtaiz\'s Ali next movie!', '', NULL, 0),
(143, 'Nirmal Purja climbing 14 highest peaks in 7 months!', 'nirmal-purja-climbing-14-highest-peaks-in-7-months!', '1', 'Nirmal Purja climbing 14 highest peaks in 7 months!', '<p>Nirmal Purja was born in Chitwan. He was selected in Gorkha Brigade in 2003 AD. He is now serving as a vital part of British Special Boat Service. After the successful expedition of summiting Mount Everest in 2019, he has climbed many peaks around the nation. Nirmal has the new record of climbing Lhotse Mountain in only 10 hours and 15 minutes breaking the old record of 20 hours. He also has a new record of climbing the Everest, Lhotse, and Makalu in 5 days. He has also made the record of climbing Summit Everest 2 times, Lhotse once and Makalu once in seventeen days, all in one season. Now, he is on a mission to summit 14 mountains above the height of 8000m around the world in 7 months. The mission is named 14/07 Project Possible. Hama Iron and Steel Industries Pvt. Ltd. together with Premier Insurance Co. (Nepal) support and encourage him. Mr. Rajan Krishna Shrestha, Managing Director of Hama Iron and Steel Industries Pvt Ltd believes that Nirmal&rsquo;s new expedition is a matter of pride and can be a great way to promote Visit Nepal 2020, as it approaching very soon. This mission of Nirmal will also be helping to uplift the tourism industry of Nepal.</p>\r\n', '6c9c5cb4bc22184560c268967862c764366160116.jpeg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-08 07:56:48', '2019-04-08 08:05:01', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, '', 'sanghars giri', '', NULL, 0),
(144, 'Vidya Balan\'s story of buying first air-conditioner!', 'vidya-balan\'s-story-of-buying-first-air-conditioner!', '1', 'Vidya Balan\'s story of buying first air-conditioner!', '<p>Vidya Balan along with doing films, she is also running a radio show. In the recent podcast of her show, Sonam Kapoor talked about financial independence. She went on describing how her father gave her wings to freedom and to make decisions. After that Vidya Balan too talked about her financial independence and recalled the story of the time when she bought her first air-conditioner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She said, &quot;I started doing ad films at the age of 19 and then I started doing it regularly and earned well. When I bought an air-conditioner for the first time through the hard earned money, that feeling was truly special.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She further added, &quot;It felt like it&#39;s not just an air-conditioner but a Kohinoor diamond that I have put up there. I can&#39;t explain that feeling in words. When one is financially independent, when they earn by themselves and splurge it, that feeling is something else.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source. Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of &quot;de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum&quot; (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, &quot;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..&quot;, comes from a line in section 1.10.32.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The standard chunk of Lorem Ipsum used since the 1500s is reproduc