(149, 'Muna Gauchan stood top 21 at Miss Eco International Nepal 2019', 'muna-gauchan-stood-top-21-at-miss-eco-international-nepal-2019', '1', 'Muna Gauchan stood top 21 at Miss Eco International Nepal 2019', '<p>Muna Gauchan, a noted model who has been chosen as an official delegate from Nepal to Miss Eco International 2019 has finished the event being on top 21 among the sixty-five delegates from different corners of the globe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the competition, she also stood in the top 15 in the talent showcase. The finale of Miss Eco International 2019 was held at Cairo Opera house, Egypt where Suheyn Cipriani of Peru was crowned as the new queen for the pageant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.glamournepal.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/muna-gauchan-2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before joining Miss Eco International 2019, Muna went through orientation and grooming session regarding the participation at international pageant conducted by choreographer Rojin Shakya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muna earned the opportunity to represent Nepal at Eco International 2019 after she has been crowned as Miss Eco International Nepal 2019 by Green Arts Media Pvt. Ltd. the franchise holder organization for the event in Nepal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.glamournepal.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/muna-gauchan-insta-pic-1.jpg\" style=\"height:810px; width:810px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>22 years of age Miss Eco International Nepal 2019, Muna Gauchan has walked dozens of times on the fashion runways, acted in the number of music videos and been caught in several TV commercials and print commercials.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The owner of slim tall figure Muna stands five feet and five inches. Been the winner of Face of Classic Diamond Jewelry 2017, Muna has graced several magazines with her beauty. The lady has also hit the silver screen of Nepali Movie industry through movies like Chapali Height 2, Jalo and Jalo return.</p>\r\n', '114618408ad9c4fc286bde01057527b9Muna-Gauchan.jpg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-08 09:50:41', '2019-04-08 17:04:08', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, '', 'sanghars giri', '', NULL, 0),
(150, 'SAFF Championship semifinal games today', 'saff-championship-semifinal-games-today', '1', 'SAFF Championship semifinal games today', '<p>Kathmandu, Sept 12 Both the semifinal matches under the SAFF Championship are taking place today in Bangladesh. Nepal is playing against the Maldives in the first semifinal match while India meets Pakistan in the next semifinal this afternoon. Both matches are taking place at the Bangabandhu Stadium in Dhaka, All Nepal Football Association (ANFA) stated. Nepal is the Group &#39;A&#39; winner while Maldives is the Group &#39;B&#39; first runner-up team. India, the winner of the Group &#39;B&#39;, is playing against Pakistan, which is the first runner-up team of Group &#39;A&#39;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nepal, which trounced Bhutan 4-0 and hosts Bangladesh 2-0 in the Group round matches, is looking for an opportunity to create history by defeating the Maldives. Acting chief coach of the Nepali football team, Bal Gopal Maharjan, expressed confidence that Nepal would get to the final and lift championship trophy as the national team is in good form. (RSS)</p>\r\n', 'ee0d18c0c557a6777c8a051df56e34bb507503702.jpeg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 'News', 'T', '1', '0', '2019-04-08 09:53:02', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '5', 0, '', 'sanghars giri', '', NULL, 1);
